    text: "xmexam.taobao.com Charlie is working with the developers as they build a new piece of software that will be able to store and retrieve data in the cloud. How does a piece of software access object, file, block, and database storage?",
    options: ["Transport", "Layer", "Security (TLS) Security Assertion Markup Language (SAML) Internet Protocol Security (IPSec)", "Application Programming Interface (API)"],
