    id: 722,
    text: "xmexam.taobao.com xmexam.taobao.com If an Internet Service Provider (ISP) fails, the customer is responsible for ensuring communication with the Cloud Service Provider (CSP). Which of the following would be the BEST strategy for ensuring that a means of communication with the CSP is always available?",
