    text: "xmexam.taobao.com xmexam.taobao.com A public cloud provider that primarily sells Platform as a Service (PaaS) deployments, both server-based and server-less, recently had a breach. The source of the breach is related to a failure that was found too late. The hypervisor that they chose to use had a vulnerability in how it managed the Central Processing Unit (CPU) utilization among the customers. What type of threat is this known as?",
