    id: 1069,
    text: "xmexam.taobao.com xmexam.taobao.com Sehaj is building a new server-based Platform as a Service (PaaS) Virtual Machine (VM). As a customer, he is concerned if the VM will be able to expand to match the needs of the users as the days go by. Which tool should he be interested in to ensure the VM is placed on the most suitable server?",
    options: ["High", "availability Distributed resource scheduling", "Dynamic optimization", "Maintenance mode"],
