    text: "xmexam.taobao.com xmexam.taobao.com A cloud administrator wants to ensure the security of a virtual server running within an Infrastructure as a Service (IaaS) environment. They would like to run a program on that virtual machine that analyzes all inbound and outbound traffic. Which of the following should this administrator use?",
