    text: "xmexam.taobao.com xmexam.taobao.com Sigrid works for a Cloud Service Provider and has been certified against ITIL. She knows that ITIL addresses the practices needed within a data center to provide the services that it needs for its customers. What is the name of the practice that ensures service will be there in the case of a horrible natural disaster that has affected the area?",
