    explanation: "Crossing over legal jurisdictions Cloud environments often span multiple countries, increasing the complexity of compliance and oversight. Challenges related to varying data privacy laws, sovereignty requirements, and cross border data transfer restrictions create hurdles for global IT that must be managed carefully. Implementing continuous monitoring is a technical and operational challenge not unique to global systems. Obtaining access logs is a common audit task in any IT environment, not a global-specific challenge. Reviewing change management procedures occurs in all audits regardless of system distribution.The Official",
