    answer: 1,
    explanation: "Quantitative assessment Two main assessment types can be used for assessing risk: Fault tree analysis is a combination of quantitative and qualitative assessments. Root cause analysis is done in problem management from ITIL. Root cause analysis analyzes why some bad event has happened so that the root cause can be found and fixed., 316-319.",
