    text: "xmexam.taobao.com xmexam.taobao.com Bola is concerned about future attacks and their ability to perform the forensic analysis that is required of him and his team for his corporation. If they move into the cloud, they are concerned they will not be able to obtain the forensic evidence that they require. Which standard provides guidelines for handling digital evidence?",
